Line x Tester data for Alpha Lattice

Source: R/alphalt.R
alphalt.Rd

The sample data containing only crosses laid out in Alpha Lattice design

data(alphalt)

Format

A data frame of five variables of 15 crosses derived from five lines and three testers.

replication

four replications

block

ten blocks

line

five inbred genotype

tester

three inbred genotype

yield

trait of intrest

Examples

results1 = ltcalpha(alphalt, replication, block, line, tester, yield)

#> 
#> Analysis of Line x Tester:  yield
